# Static archive of GameCon 2005 (reconstructed from the Internet Archive).
#
# The 2005 festival ran 7.-10. 7. 2005 in OLOMOUC (DDM, tř. 17. listopadu 47 +
# nearby university dorms). It was still run by the Altar publishing house, and
# in 2005 GameCon was a SECTION of the whole altar.cz publisher site (path
# altar.cz/gamecon/), not a standalone site or subdomain — older than the
# gamecon.altar.cz era (2006-2008).
#
# Scope: only the GameCon pages were reconstructed (the ~29 /gamecon/ pages,
# incl. the Mistrovství v DrD results archive vysledky95..vysledky04), served
# here at the root. The original /gamecon/ link prefix was rewritten to /.
# Pages were restored from web.archive.org, transcoded ISO-8859-2 -> UTF-8.
#
# The 2005 pages share Altar's global site nav, which links all over the parent
# publisher site (/altar/*, /drd/, /kontakt/, /cgi/*, the shop, etc.). Those
# cross-site links are intentionally NOT reconstructed — they fall to the themed
# 404, as does any uncaptured URL.
#
# Assets (stylesheets/default.css, img/gamecon/*) are served at their original
# absolute paths, since the pages reference them absolutely.

DirectoryIndex index.html
ErrorDocument 404 /404.html

<IfModule mod_rewrite.c>
    RewriteEngine On

    # Serve real files / dirs directly (pages at root, assets under their paths).
    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -f [OR]
    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -d
    RewriteRule ^ - [L]

    # Homepage.
    RewriteRule ^$  index.html [L]

    # Everything else (cross-site Altar chrome, uncaptured) -> themed 404.
    RewriteRule ^.*$ - [R=404,L]
</IfModule>
